caption.text:
KINJAZ audition has ended! Feeling thankful that I'm selected by them to be part of the team!

This is going to be another milestone for me, another memorable and great experience in my life!

Tomorrow will be our first rehearsal until Friday, and Saturday will be the show day ! It's going to be a crazy  week ahead because we are gonna practice so hard for this! @gottomovesg 
So guys do come down to support and watch these amazing choreographers dance.. Chances like this are hard to get.. Especially when you get to watch them live in action!

For those who didn't make it through the audition, don't think this is a failure or you aren't good enough ! (For those that make it through also , don't think we're good enough already ) Because.....The real failure only comes when you give up ( or stop work hard and stop learning ) ! So just keep learning and work hard ! At the same time always believe in yourself, we can do it ! Peace !!!! 👊🏼💪🏼🙏🏼🙌🏼 #recognizestudios #kinjaz #gottamovesg
